summary: I WAS SITTING IN THE VEHICLE PARKED WAITING FOR THE RAIN TO PASS.  FRONT WINDOW WAS CRACKED.  WHEN I HEARD A LOUD BANG.  TURNED AROUND THE BACK WINDOW ON THE DRIVER SIDE HAD SHATTERED.  THIS IS THE 3RD TIME ONE OF MY WINDOWS ON THIS CAR HAS JUST SHATTERED.  NOTHING WAS THROWN INTO THE CAR NO VEHICLES HAD DRIVEN BY.
